            "list": [
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Normal Attack</span></p><p>Deals 1 <span style=\"color: #FF9999\">Pyro DMG</span>.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/07/12/35428890/1ce09211f025bf5470682189e0837732_6229531508167966228.png",
                "id": "talent67386",
                "key": "Seal of Approval",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "pyro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Seal of Approval"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Elemental Skill</span></p><p>Deals 3 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro DMG</span> and attaches <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Scarlet Seal</span> to this character.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Scarlet Seal</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Status</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">When the character uses a Charged Attack:</span> Damage dealt +2.</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usage(s): 1</span>. (Can stack up to 2 times)</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/07/15/35428890/5bef20ac953cae4a26b35ba84c55c406_7638797100919036708.png",
                "id": "talent39453",
                "key": "Signed Edict",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "pyro"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Signed Edict"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Elemental Burst</span></p><p>Deals 3 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro DMG</span>, attaches <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Scarlet Seal</span> and <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Brilliance </span>to this character.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Scarlet Seal</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Status</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">When the character uses a Charged Attack:</span> Damage dealt +2.</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usage(s): 1</span>. (Can stack up to 2 times)</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Brilliance</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Status</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">When the character uses a Charged Attack</span>: Spend 1 less <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span>. (Once every round.)</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">End Phase</span>: Attach <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Scarlet Seal </span>to this character.</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Duration (Rounds): 2</span>.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/07/15/35428890/2c415dc76ad1e6437d2144d4c998f35b_2012904674991041699.png",
                "id": "talent58338",
                "key": "Done Deal",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "pyro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Done Deal"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>Applies Pyro and can trigger the following Elemental Reactions:</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\"> </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">]</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Melt</span>: DMG +2 for this instance</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\"> </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">]</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Vaporize</span>: DMG +2 for this instance</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\"> </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">]</span><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Overloaded</span>: DMG +2 for this instance, the target is forcibly switched to the next character</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\"> </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">Dendro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">]</span><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Burning</span>: DMG +1 for this instance, creates a [<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Burning Flame</span>] that will deal 1 Pyro DMG at the end of the Round (Takes effect once, max 2 stacks)</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/07/15/35428890/d714b3b669cc08d1d8e34464fd7a3630_3915194931750909965.png",
                "id": "talent48619",
                "key": "Pyro DMG",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Pyro DMG"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Charged Attack</span></strong></p><p>Before your Action Phase, should the total number of your Elemental Dice be even, your Normal Attack will be considered a Charged Attack.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Usage(s)</span></strong></p><p>After this card's effect is triggered, 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usage </span>of it will be consumed.</p><p>This card will be discarded immediately once it has 0 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usages </span>remaining.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Duration (Rounds)</span></strong></p><p>Each time you reach the end of a Round, <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Duration (Rounds) </span>-1.</p><p>This card will be discarded immediately once <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Duration (Rounds)</span> runs out.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/07/15/35428890/245c229cf6f7364c7c9a7aea3db1a1ad_28146934895709110.png",
